# FUTURE_CS_02

## Phishing Email Detection & Awareness System

This project was completed as part of the Future Interns Cyber Security Internship.

### Task Overview
Performed phishing email analysis and identified suspicious indicators such as:
- Fake sender addresses
- Reward scams
- Suspicious links
- Social engineering tactics

### Tools Used
- Google Phishing Quiz
- Browser Inspection Tools
- MS Word

### Outcome
Classified phishing and legitimate emails and documented cybersecurity awareness practices.
